---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const demos = [
  { title: 'Reclaim Your Time with Kalyan AI', id: 'Sx6ZVQ_EYSg' },
  { title: 'Turn Cold Lists into Hot Leads', id: '0Am1DEJEY2k' },
  { title: 'See Your Cash Before It Hits the Bank', id: '1c0JG1CSYLg' },
];
---

<Layout
	title="Kalyan AI | AI systems that help run your business"
	description="We design and run AI systems that bring in new opportunities and keep daily work under control — with people in the loop."
>
	<main class="flex flex-col gap-16">
		<section class="relative overflow-hidden px-6 py-12 md:px-10 lg:px-12">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.2] blur-3xl glow-animate bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_18%_30%,rgba(10,170,231,0.2),transparent_45%),radial-gradient(circle_at_78%_55%,rgba(171,113,247,0.18),transparent_42%)]"></div>
			<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-5xl">
				<div class="ka-card rounded-[22px] p-6 md:p-8 shadow-[0_18px_60px_-45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)] backdrop-blur">
					<div class="space-y-6 text-[var(--text)]">
						<p class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border-2 border-[var(--primary)] bg-white px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[var(--primary)]">
							AI systems, built and run with you
						</p>
							<h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[var(--brand-navy)] md:text-5xl">
								<span>AI systems that help run your business</span> <span class="text-[var(--primary)]">— without the busywork.</span>
							</h1>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-lg text-[var(--muted)] md:text-xl">
							We design and run AI systems that handle two hard parts of running a business: bringing in new opportunities and keeping day-to-day work under control — with human oversight built in.
						</p>
							<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
								<a class="rounded-full bg-[var(--accent-teal)] px-5 py-3 text-base text-center font-medium text-white shadow-sm transition duration-200 hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-[var(--secondary)]" href="/contact#book" data-plausible="BookACall">
									Book a call
								</a>
								<a href="/how-the-systems-work" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-[var(--primary)] text-[var(--primary)] rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-[var(--primary)] hover:text-white transition-colors">See how the systems work</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>


		<section id="explainer" class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">What we do in 60 seconds</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto max-w-3xl text-[var(--primary)]">
				New here? Start with this.
			</p>

			<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-black/5 shadow-sm">
				<div class="aspect-video w-full">
					<video
						class="h-full w-full"
						controls
						preload="metadata"
						playsinline
						poster="/video/kalyan-explainer.jpg"
					>
						<source src="/video/kalyan-explainer.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
						Your browser does not support the video tag.
					</video>
				</div>
			</div>
			<p class="text-sm text-[var(--muted)]">Tip: tap fullscreen for the best mobile view.</p>
		</section>

		<section class="ka-card text-center space-y-3 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 px-4 py-8 md:px-10">
			<p class="copy-narrow text-3xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Systems you can trust, built around how your business truly runs.</p>
			<p class="copy-narrow text-lg text-[var(--primary)] text-center mx-auto max-w-2xl">Clear inputs, deliberate decisions, and steady ownership—no noise added.</p>
		</section>

		<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 flex flex-col gap-6">
			<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Systems that help bring in new business</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow text-lg text-[var(--primary)] text-center block mx-auto max-w-3xl -mt-1">These systems work quietly in the background to keep new opportunities coming in and moving forward — without relying on manual chasing.</p>
				<ul class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-center text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Reach out to potential customers and respond to new enquiries</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Keep conversations going so opportunities don’t go cold</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Ask the right questions to understand fit early</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Book meetings directly into the calendar</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Keep track of who’s interested and what’s happening next</span></li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<p class="copy-narrow text-center text-lg text-[var(--primary)] mx-auto max-w-3xl">Together, these systems let the business grow without creating more work.</p>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Systems that reduce admin and give clear visibility</h2>
				<p class="copy-narrow text-lg text-[var(--primary)] text-center block mx-auto max-w-3xl -mt-1">As the business grows, these systems handle the work that normally creates noise, mess and manual effort.</p>
				<ul class="mx-auto max-w-3xl space-y-3 text-center text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Prepare proposals and documents consistently</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Track activity and results without manual reporting</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Keep cashflow and commitments visible</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Reduce inbox and spreadsheet chaos</span></li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2"><span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span><span>Highlight what needs attention before it becomes a problem</span></li>
				</ul>
			</section>
		</div>

		<div class="ka-card p-8 mb-8 text-center">
			<p class="text-sm text-[var(--primary)] font-medium mb-2">CASE STUDY</p>
			<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mb-2">Spa by Kaajal</h3>
			<p class="text-[var(--muted)] mb-4">4 hours of weekly finance admin → 30 minutes. First version live in 4 weeks.</p>
			<a href="/case-studies" class="btn-primary inline-block">See the full story →</a>
		<p class="text-[var(--primary)] text-lg italic mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--border)]">
			"I use these systems in my own businesses — I built Kalyan AI to give others the same edge."
		</p>
		<p class="text-[var(--muted)] text-base mt-2 italic" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Zax Kalyan, Founder</p>
	</div>

		<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">See it in action</h2>
			<p class="copy-narrow mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center text-[var(--primary)]">90-second snapshots of real systems</p>
			<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
				{demos.map((demo) => (
					<div class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur">
						<h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">{demo.title}</h3>
						<div class="aspect-video overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-[var(--border-subtle)] bg-black/5">
							<iframe
								class="h-full w-full"
								src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${demo.id}?rel=0&modestbranding=1`}
								title={demo.title}
								allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
								allowfullscreen
								loading="lazy"
							></iframe>
						</div>
					</div>
				))}
			</div>
		</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">How we build</h2>
				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Discover</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We learn how the business really runs and <span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">where friction slows work</span>.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Design</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We outline a hosted AI system that mirrors how you operate with <span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">clear owners</span> and guardrails.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Build</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We assemble and test the hosted layer so <span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">decisions and handoffs</span> happen reliably.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Host &amp; Improve</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We operate, <span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">monitor, and refine</span> so performance and oversight stay aligned.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card p-8 my-12 text-center">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--text)] mb-4">How engagements work</h3>
				<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Phase 1</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">First working system live in 2–4 weeks</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Operate &amp; Improve</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">We host, monitor, and refine over time</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Expand</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">Add new areas as your needs grow</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-2 text-center rounded-2xl bg-white/80 p-5 shadow-sm border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Training</p>
						<p class="copy-narrow text-[var(--muted)]">Your team learns how to use it from day one</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="space-y-6 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Built for trust</h2>
				<div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
					<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Clear ownership and approvals</p>
						<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Every decision has an owner</span>, approvals are explicit, and nothing moves without a named accountable person.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Guardrails and auditability</p>
						<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Controls, logs, and checkpoints</span> are built in so you can see what happened and why.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Evidence and reporting</p>
						<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">Signals and actions</span> are summarised into concise reports that leaders can review quickly.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Monitoring and support</p>
						<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">We host and monitor</span> the system, handle issues, and keep it aligned with your operating reality.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="space-y-1 rounded-2xl bg-white/70 p-4 text-center shadow-sm backdrop-blur border border-[var(--border-subtle)]">
						<p class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Training and handover</p>
						<p class="text-[var(--muted)]"><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--text)]">We train your team</span> and leave clear documentation so the system sticks.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="ka-card space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-white/80 p-6 text-center shadow-[0_10px_50px_-40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] backdrop-blur md:p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[var(--brand-navy)]">Outcomes you can measure</h2>
				<ul class="mx-auto space-y-2 text-center text-[var(--muted)]">
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span>
						<span><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Hours back each week</span> by removing manual handoffs and checks.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span>
						<span><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Fewer dropped balls</span>: follow-ups become a system, not a memory test.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span>
						<span><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Faster response</span> on leads and cases with clear ownership.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex items-start justify-center gap-2">
						<span class="mt-1 h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--primary)]"></span>
						<span><span class="font-semibold text-[var(--primary)]">Daily visibility</span> on progress, risks, and next actions for leaders.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
